title: FETCH QUEST - Ep. 3 - Paw & Order

description:
It's the EPIC FINALE of Fetch Quest! Our fearless pups and courageous cat claw their way out of the Cirque De May and discover the secret origin of the Very Good Boy...


This episode contains violence, profanity, sexual content, and violence towards animals.


Support the show on Patreon!

Cookie is Beth May (@heybethmay)

Theme song by Maxton Waller

Cover art by Alex Moore (@notanotheralex)
